parts.text: I will create a digital painting of a futuristic city as twilight descends. The sky will be a blend of deep purples and oranges, casting long shadows across sleek, towering skyscrapers. Numerous flying cars with bright headlights and glowing trails will zip between the buildings. The architecture will be modern and imaginative, incorporating sharp angles and smooth curves. Neon signs in various vibrant colors will adorn the buildings, illuminating the scene with a soft, artificial glow.
